DGMK Logo Deutsche Wissenschaftliche Gesellschaft für Erdöl, Erdgas und Kohle e.V. is a German national association of academics and professionals in the petroleum industry. It is based in Hamburg, Germany and the current chairman is Wilhelm Keim. The name DGMK derives from the former association name of Deutsche Gesellschaft für Mineralölwissenschaft und Kohlechemie.
